-- TPC-DS_query 15
           SELECT
             "TPC-DS Benchmark Model"."d_customer_zip_code" AS "d_customer_zip_code",
             SUM("TPC-DS Benchmark Model"."m_CS_SALES_PRICE_sum") AS "sum_m_cs_sales_price_sum_ok"
           FROM
             "TPC-DS Benchmark Model - Snowflake - 1GB"."tpc-ds benchmark model" "TPC-DS Benchmark Model"
           WHERE
                 ("TPC-DS Benchmark Model"."d_customer_zip_code" IN (
                   '80348',
                   '81792',
                   '83405',
                   '85392',
                   '85460',
                   '85669',
                   '86197',
                   '86475',
                   '88274')
               OR
                 "TPC-DS Benchmark Model"."d_customer_state" IN ('CA', 'GA', 'WA')
               OR  
                   "TPC-DS Benchmark Model"."d_catalog_sales_price_tier" = 'More than 500')
               AND
                 "TPC-DS Benchmark Model"."Sold Calendar Year" = 2001
               AND
                 "TPC-DS Benchmark Model"."Sold d_quarter_of_year" = 1
           GROUP BY
             1
           HAVING "m_CS_SALES_PRICE_sum" IS NOT NULL
           ORDER BY 1
           LIMIT 100
